Q. finding a way to maximize the number of Queens with the following condition

Queens can atack each other if they are placed diagonally.
but, we don't want to do.

Example

Input
4

Output
row pos : 0  col pos : 1
row pos : 1  col pos : 3
row pos : 2  col pos : 0
row pos : 3  col pos : 2

row pos : 0  col pos : 2
row pos : 1  col pos : 0
row pos : 2  col pos : 3
row pos : 3  col pos : 1

the number of ways = 2

